Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:52.29,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾澀了它的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.15,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}剎那間被誘惑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:59.71,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在欺騙的愛中沉淪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:06.65,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,5000)\an2}Get out……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:15.61,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望揮舞純真無邪之劍的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:21.24,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}盡情地讓疼痛貫穿我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:21.48,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an1}Just say you love me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:23.53,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}You know I've got a crush on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:27.09,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天使般的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:29.94,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}比蜜還甜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:35.47,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}設下愛情的陷阱（感受吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:43.67,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“汝那罪惡的愛情觀　現在立刻悔改吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:46.19,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}純潔地將你引導
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:51.62,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想用純潔的靈魂抱緊你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是旋風管家第二夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家覺得怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鶇琉璃真的很強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是能使用西斯特瑪的獨行軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  她的目的到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相當讓人在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後下一回是全新的展開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於輪到大家翹首以盼的那一位出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,劇場究竟將會如何發展
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而我又要遭到怎麼樣的不測呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次大家再踩得更結實一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}那之後過了25分鐘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}小桂還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}她頭腦冷靜些了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.41,0:23:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}是啊  總麼說也是在雪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}要是頭腦能冷靜些下來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}那是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}酒在哪裡！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}居然！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}綾崎同學  你居然騙了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}啊  又中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}又中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.13,0:23:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}好  來做吧
